# Phase 10: Multi-Monitor Projection Support

Implement a dual-monitor projection system where "Monitor 1" is optimized for streaming/OBS and "Monitor 2" is dedicated to extended display projection. Each monitor will support independent presentation presets.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Monitor Detection**: I will use the `screen_retriever` package to detect connected displays. Monitor 2 will automatically target the first available non-primary display.
> **Window Communication**: `desktop_multi_window` will be used to sync lyrics and settings from the main dashboard to the projector windows.

